               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; names of the donors; name of the scribe; name of the king; a few lines on the incipit page of the Text, alternating with black lines; incipit of each section of the text; abbreviations; elements of Ethiopic numerals; elements of the punctuation signs; some other words, e.g., halle luya (e.g., fols. 4rb, 4vb, 5ra), ṣällǝyu (e.g., fols. 9va, 11va), nǝbäl (e.g., fols. 9vb, 10va), wä-kaʿǝbä (e.g., fols. 10ra, 11ra), ʾǝgäle (e.g., fols. 37vb), wä-ʾǝmzǝ (e.g., fols. 70vab, 71rab).</rubric>
                     <incipit>
