                        <item xml:id="e1">- Erasures: e.g., fols. 16va, 27ra, 87va.&#xD;
- Omitted letters or words are written interlineally or in the margin: e.g., fols. 14ra, 25rb, 26vb, 27vb, 31va.&#xD;
