- The word እገሌ is marked above and below by dashes in red and black ink: e.g., fols. 52vb, 53rab, 53vab, 54rab, or by thin lines, e.g. fols. 103vab, 104rab.&#xD;
- Pen trial: 113v.&#xD;
- Scribbles and doodles: e.g., fols. 2r, 112v, 113r, 114r, 114v.&#xD;
- Sign, in the shape of a cross with a loop at the end of each arm, written in the margin: fols. 29v, 69r, 93v.</item>
